For more information, view the iv(1) man page.

Changes
=======
For a list of changes in this and all previous versions of iv,
please see the ``NEWS`` file.

Bugs
====
Current bugs can be viewed in the `issue tracker
<http://github.com/bytbox/iv/issues>`__ on github. Bugs and feature requests
may be reported to the same place.

